projetos.title: Technical Specifications
projetos.description: The walnut wood card tray is precision milled to perfectly fit a stack of Focus cards. The powder coated steel divider separates active cards from new ones, or can be used to archive important task lists.

specs.title: Material
specs.description: Solid walnut base with rare earth magnets and powder coated steel card cover
